#clear nuru
!nuru;Null Rune - 1 Mana per shot.
!firu;Fire Rune - 2 Mana per shot.
!icru;Ice Rune - 2 Mana per shot.
!boru;Bolt Rune - 2 Mana per shot.
!acru;Acid Rune - 2 Mana per shot.
/i
#runea
:spella
#clear s
